This is a fork from https://bitbucket.org/zalew/django-online-status

Because it was not updated from the py hosted from 2014, I have to fork it here to update it for my project. Free to use if it could help.

========================
django-online-status
========================

Online status for authenticated users (online, idle, offline) and list of current users online, all to display with templatetags. No database models, everything cached.
Read more: http://bitbucket.org/zalew/django-online-status/wiki/Home